title: Here we go!
body:
I finished painting Ellie!!!

Know what that means?????

Its Arthurian Legend time!!! Still waiting on my paper to be delivered. I will be working on a larger size. 

These paintings will take longer than normal not only because of the size but because of the amount of details and I really want them to turn out good. 

If anyone is interested I can also livestream my process, sometimes. No worries if you miss a stream or if I decide not to stream, I will post WIP’s.

Sooooooo first up is Uther Pendragon. I will post the first wip Saturday or sometime next week.
